"},{"pid":"e134254a1ad52df26e5e1958e682ed0491456050","tid":1460924,"uid":173817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"立場歸隊入機場"},{"pid":"3ffa141023ab828f2d14526007ce4f5a03753b55","tid":1460924,"uid":258792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:02:28.000Z","msg":"收工黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65432067af91a68d26938e00ea49a7789458f5a9","tid":1460924,"uid":254361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n行動前，用腦諗下，要自主思考呀<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n同埋連登被滲透之下<br />\n各種謠言滿天飛，更加要冷靜思考<br />\n要多方面去驗證嗰篇文是否真實<br />\n再去諗下佢發呢個信息個目的係乜嘢<br />\n諗下佢背後有沒隱藏的意思（例如恐慌、煽動、造謠）<br />\n<br />\n和理非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」「V怪客」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里的大反派說了這麼幾句<br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以用你的力量與聲音，用你的方法去「抗爭」<br />\n力量聲音沒分大細，沒分方法嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（細音說，方法有分成本與效益）<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"7c44742159ebe4ef5c6184fe19c1cde362871fd0","tid":1460924,"uid":44174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:02:51.000Z","msg":"請歸隊!"},{"pid":"c7e3c34a98eb9df82d6888ea7c9701c362f0d866","tid":1460924,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"等放工時間歸隊"},{"pid":"3c2badbf6b234c0787ae2d0c76290c9eb4f8f891","tid":1460924,"uid":34487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:03:36.000Z","msg":"黎緊"},{"pid":"d74e4a121c0b05c33c0007ddbce8ca673146c32b","tid":1460924,"uid":292622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:04:07.000Z","msg":"入緊"},{"pid":"b34278908257a704c577493111f7f326fc8b9d66","tid":1460924,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f754e7f532e3eb71d85d52a1ebfc83f7d93609b9","tid":1460924,"uid":125026,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:27:16.000Z","msg":"一架手推車等於兩個人嘅身位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十個人推車就等於有三十個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:05:44.000Z","msg":"我要坐飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要拉喼喼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3a698c4630dafebb89df464e892f854a0bc246","tid":1460924,"uid":107596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"香港人例遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb